Introduction

A client that has had experience managing multiple gym facilities is looking to branch off and start his own establishment. He
has most of the aspects business plan laid out, however, he needs consulting regarding a more specific location for his
gym. The client has already determined he will open the gym in his hometown of Ponce, Puerto Rico. Ponce is divided
in 30 Barrios that we can choose from in regards to the placement of this establishment. Our job is to leverage existing data, 
geolocation, and clustering techniques so as to determine the optimal location for his business. 

